@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<style>
    body {
        background-color: #000;
        color: #fff;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    header {
        background-color: #00ffcc;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
        color: #000;
        font-size: 36px;
    }

    .about-us-content {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    h2 {
        color: #00ffcc;
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    ul {
        list-style-type: square;
        margin-left: 20px;
    }

        ul li {
            font-size: 16px;
        }

    footer {
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #00ffcc;
        padding: 10px;
        color: #000;
        font-size: 14px;
    }
</style>

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<main class="about-us-content">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
        At TowelMart, our mission is to provide the finest quality towels to our customers while maintaining the highest standards of service and customer satisfaction.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>
        TowelMart was founded in 2023 with a simple idea: to offer premium towels that combine comfort, durability, and style. Over the years, we've grown into a trusted provider of towels for homes, hotels, and businesses worldwide.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Values</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Quality: We are committed to delivering towels that meet the highest quality standards.</li>
        <li>Customer Satisfaction: Your satisfaction is our top priority, and we strive to exceed your expectations.</li>
        <li>Sustainability: We are dedicated to eco-friendly practices and sustainable sourcing.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Our Team</h2>
    <p>
        Our team consists of passionate individuals who share a love for fine textiles and a dedication to providing the best towels in the market. Meet our team members:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Nicolas Moreno Cordoba - Founder and CEO</li>
        <li>Randy Cantillo - Head of Product Development</li>
        <li>Nicholas Cordouba - Inversionist</li>
    </ul>
</main>

